# Public sharing rule
# Only these two code folders are allowed to be tracked for students.
*
!.gitignore
!code_soram/
!code_soram/**
!code_simulation/
!code_simulation/**

# Never share secrets or machine-specific files, even inside allowed folders.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/secrets.*
**/*secret*
**/*token*

# Python/runtime generated files
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache/